  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">2020 ERFS, implemented by Goal. Key activities included emergency responses:  to support health centres to screen malnutrition in children under five, in Zimbabwe; a multi-country ERFS across five countries to counter transmission of Covid-19: Malawi, Uganda, Niger, Iraq and Honduras; cash response to address urgent needs of vulnerable households (IDPs and refugees) already affected by Covid-19 restrictions in Iraq ; cash response to vulnerable displaced by Hurricane Eta in Honduras.</narrative>
